Package: col2hex2col
Type: Package
Title: Convert Between Color Names and Hex Codes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Antti", "Rask", email = "anttilennartrask@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides simple functions to convert between R color names and
    hexadecimal color codes. The package includes bidirectional conversion
    functions that work with single colors or vectors of colors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
